**Summary:**
This documentation explains troubleshooting mobile attribution events (install/uninstall) in Amplitude, focusing on how the Attribution API maps events from mobile attribution partners using advertising IDs (IDFA/IDFV/ADID) to existing Amplitude users within a 72-hour retention window.

